git clone https://github.com/ravinet/mahimahi
cd mahimahi
./autogen.sh
./configure
make
sudo make install
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To verify that mahimahi is successfully installed and working fine, follow the below steps: 
1. sudo sysctl -w net.ipv4.ip_forward=1
2. mm-delay 40  --> after running this command you should be able to enter the delay shell
3. then try to ping google.com if works fine then okay otherwise look at below steps.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
In case of errors:
1. If error occurs after running ./configure and the error contains a keyword like 'Werror' then follow below steps:
	sudo nano configure.ac
	PICKY_CXXFLAGS="-pedantic -Wall -Wextra -Weffc++ -Werror"   ---> Remove -Werror from this 
	make
	sudo make install
2. If successful installation is done but pinging to google fails then run.
	sudo ufw disable

